  33:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c **** 
  34:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c **** /**
  35:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   @ingroup groupCmplxMath
  36:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****  */
  37:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c **** 
  38:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c **** /**
  39:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   @defgroup cmplx_conj Complex Conjugate
  40:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c **** 
  41:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   Conjugates the elements of a complex data vector.
  42:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c **** 
  43:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   The <code>pSrc</code> points to the source data and
  44:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   <code>pDst</code> points to the destination data where the result should be written.
  45:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   <code>numSamples</code> specifies the number of complex samples
  46:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   and the data in each array is stored in an interleaved fashion
  47:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   (real, imag, real, imag, ...).
  48:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   Each array has a total of <code>2*numSamples</code> values.
  49:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c **** 
  50:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   The underlying algorithm is used:
  51:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   <pre>
  52:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   for (n = 0; n < numSamples; n++) {
  53:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****       pDst[(2*n)  ] =  pSrc[(2*n)  ];    // real part
  54:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****       pDst[(2*n)+1] = -pSrc[(2*n)+1];    // imag part
  55:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   }
  56:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   </pre>
  57:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c **** 
  58:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   There are separate functions for floating-point, Q15, and Q31 data types.
  59:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****  */
  60:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c **** 
  61:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c **** /**
  62:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   @addtogroup cmplx_conj
  63:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   @{
  64:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****  */
  65:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c **** 
  66:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c **** /**
  67:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   @brief         Floating-point complex conjugate.
  68:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   @param[in]     pSrc        points to the input vector
  69:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   @param[out]    pDst        points to the output vector
  70:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****   @param[in]     numSamples  number of samples in each vector
  71:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c ****  */
  72:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/ComplexMathFunctions/arm_cmplx_conj_f32.c **** 
